    <description><![CDATA[
        <h1>LayUI</h1>
        <br/>
        <p><b>A Layui framework completion using plug-ins</b></p>
        <br/>
        <p>The plug-in uses the Layui front-end framework to develop the page automatically completes the commonly used
            module code in the framework, and develops faster and more efficiently</p>
        <br/>
        <p><b>Plug-in for Layui front-end framework for easy development</b></p>
        <br>
        <p><a href="https://www.layui.com/doc/">LayUI 官方文档</a></p>
        <br>
        <p>Follow me on Github: <a href="https://github.com/Neroxiezi"><b>@PFinal南丞</b></a></p>
        <img src="https://nero_xeizi.gitee.io/pic/help.gif" alt="">
        ]]>
  </description>
